data.description: Move in Ready! Greenbelt! This 2020 one-story home boasts 4 bedrooms and 2 baths, 9-foot ceilings with 2-inch faux wood, open floor plan, white cabinets with hardware with with pull-out shelves.  Stainless steel appliances and an oversized island, separate shower and garden tub, while the double vanity sinks. Some of the upgrades include installed towel racks, vanity mirrors, light fixtures and shelves in the primary closet.  Luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout except for the primary closet and the garage floor and main entrance have been treated with epoxy coating.  This home comes with sprinkler system, solar screens, solar shade and full gutters.  Why chose a newer home or wait for a 2023 model? Less than a mile from the Cibolo YMCA and downtown Cibolo, where you can find restaurants, shops and more. Close proximity to JBSA Randolph.  Your dream home is here - seize it today!
